useful helper scripts for all purposes
see the documentation in each file for
installation and usage

for installation, invoke the script installme.sh
from the nesono-bin directory or...

add the following lines to your ~/.profile

# the nesono script directory
if [ -d ~/nesono-bin ]; then
  export PATH=$PATH:~/nesono-bin
fi

# and copy inputrc and vimrc
cp .inputrc ~/
cp .vimrc   ~/
